                <p>Name of Promoter: SSK Infinity Ventures LLP<br/>Registered Address: 750, 33rd A Cross, 9th Main, Jayanagar 4th Block, Jayanagar III Block, Jayanagar Police Station, Bangalore South, Bangalore - 560011, Karnataka, India<br/>Email (Grievance / Data Protection): pampannabe@gmail.com</p>
